  "subject": "[CDS] Bump CDS versions for RC1 bug fixes",
  "commit_message": "[CDS] Bump CDS versions for RC1 bug fixes\n\nBump CDS images to version 1.1.2 to install bug fixes discovered between\nM3 and RC1.  The set of bug fixes included can be found in this\nJira link: https://jira.onap.org/issues/?filter=12492\n\nIssue-ID: CCSDK-3239\nIssue-ID: CCSDK-3232\nIssue-ID: CCSDK-3230\nIssue-ID: CCSDK-3221\nIssue-ID: CCSDK-3220\nIssue-ID: CCSDK-3219\nIssue-ID: CCSDK-3211\nIssue-ID: CCSDK-3216\n\nSigned-off-by: Dan Timoney <dtimoney@att.com>\nChange-Id: Ib349918c57e7ce909c2f97d55de96bf2e0dd7c08\n(cherry picked from commit d6f0b023ce7a0e49ee1ba3236d8491ee6beb5e3c)\n",
